=== DESIGN DECISIONS ===
- Global broadcast with (session_id, payload) tuples; per-connection filter by URL session id — simple, matches “tokio broadcast” acceptance; multi-tenant scale-out would need Redis/pubsub in future.
- Session lifecycle events only from worker pull/complete paths (not every possible session patch) to match v1 engine behavior.
- job_completed payload includes worker_reported success/failed string from request body.
- No DB migrations (in-memory hub only).

